title: Black Percent of Population
description: Percent of the tract population that is Black alone&#x002C not Hispanic or Latino.

title: Asian-American Percent of Population
description: Percent of the tract population that is Asian-American alone&#x002C not Hispanic or Latino.

title: Latino Percent of Population
description: The percentage of the population that is Hispanic or Latino.

title: White Percent of Population
description: Percent of the tract population that is White alone&#x002C not Hispanic or Latino.

title: Percent of County Voting Age Citizens
description: The number of citizens in this tract who are voting age divided by the county's total number of voting age citizens.

title: Percent of County Workers
description: The percent of employed county residents in a tract out of the total employed county residents in the county.

title: Percent of Eligible Voters Not Registered
description: The percentage of voting age citizens who are not registered to vote.

title: Disabilities Percent of Population
description: The percentage of the population that is disabled.

title: Latino Percent of Population
description: The percentage of the population that is Hispanic or Latino.

title: Limited English Proficient Percent of Population
description: The percentage of the population that has limited English proficiency.

title: Percent of Population with Vehicle Access
description: The percentage of the population with access to a vehicle.

title: Percent of the Population in Poverty
description: The percentage of the population with income below the poverty level.

title: Youth Percent of Population
description: The percentage of the population between the age of 18 and 24 years old.

title: 2020 Voting Location Voter Percentage
description: The number of voters who voted at a polling place divided by the total number of voters who voted at a polling place in the county.

title: Population Density
description: The total population density per square kilometer.

title: Vote by Mail Rate (Asian-American)
description: The percentage of Asian-American voters who voted by mail.

title: Vote by Mail Rate (Latino)
description: The percentage of Latino voters who voted by mail.

title: Vote by Mail Rate (Total)
description: The percentage of voters who voted by mail.

title: Vote by Mail Rate (Youth)
description: The percentage of voters between the age of 18 and 24 years old who voted by mail.
